HEADWORD: bloodcurdling
<hw>blood"curd*ling</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>causing sudden intense
fear due to an apprehension of imminent bodily harm, to oneself or
others.</def> <illu>Awakened by a <ex>bloodcurdling</ex> scream from
right outside her window</illu>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hair-raising, nightmarish.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

